STATE OF OREGON, Respondent, v. HOMERO PRUNEDA GARZA, Appellant. (90CR-0175; CA A67854) 825 P2d 299 Gary D. Babcock, Salem, for petition. PER CURIAM

On appellant’s petition for reconsideration filed September 25, 1991,

petition for reconsideration allowed; former opinion (108 Or App 575, 815 P2d 723) reversed and remanded with instructions to dismiss indictment February 26, 1992

Before Warren, Presiding Judge, and Riggs and Edmonds, Judges.
